  "body": "#### System information\r\n\r\nGeth version: 1.10.6-stable\r\nOS & Version: ubuntu 20.04\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\n```\r\n> tx =eth.getTransactionFromBlock('0xfddbc9d9a6155c54f18f83d230996366f35ead00741e082fadc71c0497f5a6ea', 83)\r\n> eth.estimateGas({from:tx.from,to:tx.to,value:tx.value,nonce:tx.nonce,data:tx.input}, '0xfddbc9d9a6155c54f18f83d230996366f35ead00741e082fadc71c0497f5a6ea')\r\n[a number]\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\n```\r\n> tx =eth.getTransactionFromBlock('0xfddbc9d9a6155c54f18f83d230996366f35ead00741e082fadc71c0497f5a6ea', 83)\r\n> eth.estimateGas({from:tx.from,to:tx.to,value:tx.value,nonce:tx.nonce,data:tx.input}, '0xfddbc9d9a6155c54f18f83d230996366f35ead00741e082fadc71c0497f5a6ea')\r\nError: getDeleteStateObject (8688a84fcfd84d8f78020d0fc0b35987cc58911f) error: no suitable peers available\r\n        at web3.js:6357:37(47)\r\n        at web3.js:5091:62(37)\r\n        at <eval>:1:16(20)\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour\r\n\r\n`--syncmode light`, enter above in console once connected\r\n",
